==Showdown==
===Confronting the killer===
* '''Player:''' Show yourself you coward!
* '''Killer:''' So we meet at last. I have to say, I'm impressed you worked out my riddles.
* '''Player:''' Well maybe you aren't as smart as you think you are.
* '''Killer:''' Oh really? All the dead bodies suggest otherwise. And what did you do to stop them?
* '''Killer:''' NOTHING!
* '''Killer:''' People think you are some big hero but you're not. All you adventurers are the same. Nothing but opportunists!
* '''Player:''' What are you going on about?
* '''Killer:''' Well, I did have this big speech planned out but quite frankly I don't think you are worth the effort it would take to deliver it.
* '''Killer:''' So, this is the end of the line for you. It is time for the final act. The showdown. The finale. Let's see if you are up to the challenge!
* {{tact|end}}

