* '''Killer:''' Urgh...I think I may have underestimated you.
* '''Player:''' You've lost at your own game. And now it is time to see who you really are under that mask!
* {{qact|The player unmasks the killer, revealing Abigale as the culprit.}}
* '''Player:''' No! You!? But why!? Why on earth would you kill all your friends!? Why beg me to come here to help them!?
* '''Abigale:''' You just don't get it do you?
* '''Abigale:''' So big headed. So used to it all being about you. About you saving the day.
* '''Abigale:''' Well I'm sick of it!
* '''Player:''' What do you mean?
* '''Abigale:''' Adventurers! You're all the same. Everything always has to be about you.
* '''Player:''' I don't understand?
* '''Abigale:''' Of course you wouldn't! Because you can't see past yourself!
* '''Abigale:''' Believe it or not... I used to be like you.
* '''Abigale:''' I'd hear about some damsel in distress and go to help. To have my moment. For me to be the hero, just for once.
* '''Abigale:''' But YOU! You and every other darned adventurer! Every time I get there to help, it's too late. Crisis solved. Disaster averted. Reward claimed. Every time you and those other adventurers steal my moment!
* '''Abigale:''' But not this time!
* '''Abigale:''' This time, it is all about me! I'm the star of the show! ME ME ME ME ME!
* '''Player:''' Well not any longer. The show is over, and there will be no curtain call.
* '''Abigale:''' Oh, but there is always a curtain call.
* {{qact|Another killer comes out of the closest near the door.}}
* '''Player:''' What!? How!? There was another killer!?
* '''Abigale:''' Of course. Every good show needs a good supporting actor. Now, take off your mask darling. Take a bow. You have earned it.
* '''Killer:''' Of course, my love.
* {{qact|The killer unmasks himself, revealing Hewey as the culprit.}}
* '''Player:''' You!? But how!? You were almost dead when I saw you! I saw your wounds!
* '''Hewey:''' No, what you watched was what we wanted you to watch. A masterful performance if I do say myself.
* '''Player:''' But what is in this for you?
