* '''Player:''' But your friends?
* '''Player:''' They didn't deserve to die!
* '''Abigale:''' Perhaps not, but neither did I deserve to be cast back into the shadows when I deserve the spotlight!
* '''Hewey:''' Yes, while we deserve the spotlight.
* '''Abigale:''' And now I have my starring role!
* '''Hewey:''' OUR starring role.
* '''Abigale:''' Gielinor will forever remember this night and what I have done here.
* '''Hewey:''' No, what WE have done!
* '''Abigale:''' Quiet Hewey! This is my moment!
* '''Hewey:''' No, this is supposed to be our moment! It isn't just all about you either! We were in this together!
* '''Abigale:''' Stop ruining this Hewey! I have worked so hard for this and I'm not going to let you take it away from me!
* '''Hewey:''' Well I'm not going to be pushed aside either, we were both in this as equals!
* '''Abigale:''' We were never equals! How could you possibly compare to me!?
* '''Hewey:''' You egotistical, selfish...
* {{qact|Abigale stabs Hewey.}}
* '''Hewey:''' No...my love...
* {{qact|Hewey dies.}}
* '''Abigale:''' No....no...what have I done!?
* '''Abigale:''' It wasn't supposed to be like this...but you just couldn't let me have my moment. WHY HEWEY WHY!? I loved you...
